---
title: Falafel Bites & Roast Veggie Couscous with Creamy Pesto Yoghurt & Toasted Almonds
description: What's a quick and easy way to bring a new burst of life to a dish? Add a fresh squeeze of lemon juice and colourful roasted
veggies to couscous; it adds an extra hit of flavour with every bite! Teamed with warm falafel bites and pesto yoghurt, this dish is
all kinds of yum.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spinach-falafel-pumpkin-couscous-6d781196.jpg
